Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00013%2F1487095482887&h=63e89ffd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00013/1487095482887</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 湖南省婁底市漣源市斗笠山鎮祖保煤礦發生爆炸事故，救援人員接報到場搜救，救出4名被困人員，惟事故造成9人死亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00178_019.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=57d87fe2\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_019.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 黑龍江省大慶市大批市民上街示威抗議中國忠旺鋁業在當地建廠造成環境污染，部份示威者更聚集市政府前抗議，當局出動大批警力戒備，官方回應指若環保問題不過關絕不允許施工。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00013/1487095485601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00013%2F1487095485601&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=847f2a3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00013%2F1487095485601&h=895ed41e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00013/1487095485601</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_014.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00178_014.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5dc63d3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_014.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 黑龍江哈爾濱的霽虹橋有關工程日前展開，以便將高鐵引入市區，多名市民手持橫額到施工現場抗議，指工程是公然破壞全國重點保護的一級文物。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549872&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549872%26target%3D2&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1e32b26a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549872%26target%3D2&h=7eba03f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549872&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 就3年前高雄強冠公司的黑心油案件，法庭判強冠公司賠償其中160人每人六千至九千元不等，合計133萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00178_010.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5b509be4\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00178_010.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 由東方電氣（廣州）重型機器有限公司自主設計及製造的低壓加熱器在廣州裝運出口運往法國，該設備將用於法國電力集團CPI系列核電站的設備更換。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549881&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549881%26target%3D2&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f86c9e43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549881%26target%3D2&h=95e4dbc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549881&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)"},{"pid":"76b159b6a044b60ffd0e447499c1f7fc4718f9c8","tid":120941,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:37:45.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 韓國、馬來西亞多家傳媒及路透社等引述消息指朝鮮領袖金正恩的同父異母兄長金正男在馬來西亞吉隆坡機場遭朝鮮女特工暗殺身亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00014/1487095491280\" data-s