419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 白宮國家安全顧問弗林被揭發在總統特朗普宣誓就職前與俄羅斯官員秘密討論奧巴馬政府對俄羅斯的制裁問題，弗林最終宣佈辭職，由退休將領凱洛格（Keith Kellogg）暫代空缺。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00014/1487095502668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00014%2F1487095502668&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=eb78f79f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00014%2F1487095502668&h=9b015528\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00014/1487095502668</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00180_012.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5aa7824f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_012.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549848&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549848%26target%3D2&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0bc3d504\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549848%26target%3D2&h=38844005\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549848&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170215/19928707?_ga=1.137772272.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170215%2F19928707%3F_ga%3D1.137772272.1316658954.1419942048&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ac114e2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170215%2F19928707%3F_ga%3D1.137772272.1316658954.1419942048&h=66a8a349\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170215/19928707?_ga=1.137772272.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 美國財政部指控委內瑞拉副總統阿薩米（Tareck El Aissami）及其商界友人貝略（Samark Jose Lopez Bello）為可卡因販毒商，決定凍結兩人在美國的資產及列入制裁名單。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00014/1487095498643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00014%2F1487095498643&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c7535bdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00014%2F1487095498643&h=9a84d16f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00014/1487095498643</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00180_033.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1f054dd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_033.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 日本首相安倍晉三日訪美回國後表示釣魚島（日稱尖閣諸島）適用於《美日安保條約》已成定案，往後不需要再與美方確認，日本文部科學省隨即要求全部中小學教科書列出釣魚島是日本的「固有領土」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_016.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00180_016.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5c312497\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_016.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 南韓曾接連有養牛場爆出口蹄疫情的忠清北道報恩郡再有3個養牛場爆出口蹄疫症，令全南韓的口蹄疫個案在本月內增至9宗。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_021.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00180_021.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3e4dada5\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_021.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 美國加州奧羅維爾大壩（Oroville）的主要洩洪道曾出現一個巨型決口，導致廿萬居民緊急疏散，經過當局持續洩洪，水位已經回落，暫時解除大壩崩塌的危機。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_028.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170215%2F00180_028.html&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=32c549a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170215/00180_028.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊集中帖<br />\n(想了解呢個post既來歷,檢索返以往既每日用2分鐘睇新聞,可以入去呢條link):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/57314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/57314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日新聞<br />\n(想追返尋日既post就入去):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/119541/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/119541/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Facebook Page<br />\n(如果想係facebook睇既歡迎like下,每日朝早9點post每日新聞,方便大家係facebook都睇到):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkintelligentsiaplatform/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.